This paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-category as it deals with the diversity-multiplexing tradeoff for communication systems. It may also belong to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-category as it discusses communication protocols. The Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper deals with the control of communication systems. The Communications (cs.COMM) and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories are also possible as the paper deals with communication systems.
